The paper discusses the security concerns of Machine Learning-as-a-Service (MLaaS) systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of active learning techniques in model extraction attacks, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses possible defense strategies, which falls under the categories of data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE).
